  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess the short term success and feasibility of ileal
      transposition with sleeve gastrectomy in non-morbidly obese patients with poorly controlled
      Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
